  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Naussilus.Core::Naussilus.Core.VisualNovels.EventDatas.DialogueDatas.DialogueData
  <Lines>k__BackingField:
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 292bca25009c3b846973697c392c826a, type: 2}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 368af27e801a8f643a3763179d93db07, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - "Ben j\u2019\xE9tais s\xFBr de gagner, j'avais toutes les cartes en main, et
      au final elle \xE0 raffl\xE9 la mise."
    - Il y a quelque chose qui cloche.
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 292bca25009c3b846973697c392c826a, type: 2}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3d35d0e1530830e42b12a5e80d0329dc, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - "Et franchement, entre nous, jamais une femme m\u2019battrais \xE0 la loyale."
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c468415a02cbf74438a48816b0fe1fa6, type: 2}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f0358eca1d351f540a61dc689202b2b8, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - "Oh ! Tu oses m\u2019insulter comme \xE7a ?"
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c468415a02cbf74438a48816b0fe1fa6, type: 2}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3973df86522e4b743879172e3518e737, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - "J\u2019ai plut\xF4t l\u2019impression que cette d\xE9faite t\u2019a piqu\xE9
      dans ton ego, Herlock."
  <Answers>k__BackingField:
